      <h1 id="personal-loan-vs-credit-card-malaysia-complete-comparison-guide-2024">Personal Loan vs Credit Card Malaysia: Complete Comparison Guide 2024</h1>
<p>Choosing between a personal loan and credit card in Malaysia can impact your finances for years. Both options offer quick access to funds, but they work very differently. This guide compares every aspect to help you make the right choice.</p>
