<ul>
<li>Diversifies your credit mix</li>
<li>Shows ability to handle installment debt</li>
<li>Improves score through consistent payments</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Negative Effects</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Initial credit inquiry may lower score temporarily</li>
<li>High debt-to-income ratio concerns lenders</li>
<li>Late payments severely damage credit rating</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="credit-card-credit-impact">Credit Card Credit Impact</h3>
